<typeStatus box="[352,450,727,752]" pageId="5" pageNumber="476">holotype</typeStatus>
has been collected late October at the altitude of about 
<quantity box="[1073,1161,728,752]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7" pageId="5" pageNumber="476" unit="m" value="2700.0">2700 m</quantity>
